# HTTPS Enforcement - Redirect all HTTP traffic to HTTPS
# IMPORTANT: Replace 'yourdomain.com' with your actual domain before deployment
# For Netlify: Replace with your Netlify domain (e.g., 'amazing-site.netlify.app')
# For custom domains: Use your actual domain name
http://yourdomain.com/* https://yourdomain.com/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback for client-side routing
/*    /index.html   200